{"tid":2085232,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"承被捕手足及犧牲烈士之志，以重光香港為己任","createTime":"2020-06-29T18:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T04:02:23.000Z","uid":309398,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ddeb016233f466b698689aff9a0a9e80b8d0c6e0","tid":2085232,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:20:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">自2019年港人奮起抵抗惡法，各司其職而同心同德，竭力爭取五大訴求。惟過程艱鉅，被捕手足無數、犧牲烈士難以盡錄，只換來撤回條例。港共致力分化人民，黑警及黑勢力目無法紀，以恫嚇市民為首要任務，令和平抗爭者心力交瘁，運動氣氛一度式微。但本人仍充滿信心立下誓言：</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">於2020年7月1日之後仍堅持反共立場，繼續對抗《國安法》及其他惡法，承被捕手足及犧牲烈士之志，以重光香港為己任，期望終有一天將史上最不公義的集團從香港土地上趕絕，還香港人煲底之約。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">此誓。</span></strong></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"368a6ecf80a4dd3787d16fba6534445c7fdf6f2a","tid":2085232,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:34:22.000Z","msg":"習主席!就是他!"},{"pid":"2b42b811b75f55fd3c1fa575ae8883280181c251","tid":2085232,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:52:03.000Z","msg":"一人一post推71<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Facebook ig airdrop</span></span>"},{"pid":"978ce451d2cdaeb866b18d72f5853b747bfc4f2d","tid":2085232,"uid":27250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T20:03:09.000Z","msg":"毋忘烈士之志，終身以核平支那為志以報家毀之仇"},{"pid":"e5d438426e336fc0e978136e2d1b3c0d9731a9e8","tid":2085232,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"368a6ecf80a4dd3787d16fba6534445c7fdf6f2a","tid":2085232,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:34:22.000Z","msg":"習主席!就是他!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"仆你個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" clas